<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Albrecht II. Kolowrat, Hauptmann im Elbogner Land</head><p>Der Rat wird nach Rückkehr mehrerer Ratsherren wegen Andres Steinpach d. J. und dem offenen Brief des Adressaten antworten und gibt dem Boten den offenen Brief zurück.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_102" id="49v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_102_r1l16"><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>Albr<ex>echten</ex></expan> <expan>Colobrat<ex>en</ex></expan> Hauptman </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l17">in <expan>Ellenpognerlant<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_102_r1l19"> <expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> / als Jr vns 
<del rend="strikethrough">geſchriben habt </del> . von Endres Steinpachs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l20">
<add><expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan></add> vnd vns auch 
<del rend="strikethrough">er </del> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> offenbrief damit geſant habt / . daʒ haben wir wol </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_line_1574776659705_648"> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / Vnd laſʒen 
<del rend="strikethrough">euch </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_102_line_1574776654926_643"><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> Edell </ab></add> wiſʒen . / daʒ etlıch vnſers Rats / cʒu <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒeit nicht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l25">anheim ſein / vnd wenn die herheim kumen / ſo 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſol </del> vvollen wir euch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l26">dann ein antvvurt laſʒen bey vnſer ſelbs botſchaft . Vnd haben auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_102_r1l27"> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> boten 
<add><ab facs="#facs_102_line_1574776766913_669"><expan>denſelb<expan>e</expan>n</expan> </ab></add> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> offenbrief wider geben . <expan>Dat<expan>um</expan></expan> Jn die <expan>ſ<expan>an</expan>c<expan>t</expan>i</expan> Egidij </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_102" id="49v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Albr<ex>echten</ex></expan>
<expan>Colobrat<ex>en</ex></expan>, hauptman in
                                <expan>Ellenpognerlant<ex>en</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her
                                                  <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan>, als ir uns von
                                                Endres Steinpachs <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>
<add><expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan></add> und
                                                uns auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> offenbrief
                                                damit gesant habt, daz haben wir wol
                                                  <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und laszen
                                                  <add><expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> edell</add>
                                                wiszen, daz etlich unsers rats czu
                                                  <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> czeit nicht anheim
                                                sein und wenn die herheim kumen, so wollen wir euch
                                                dann ein antwurt laszen bey unser selbs botschaft
                                                und haben auch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> boten
                                                  <add><expan>denselb<expan>e</expan>n</expan></add>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> offenbrief wider geben.
                                                  <expan>Dat<expan>um</expan></expan> in die
                                                  <expan>s<expan>an</expan>c<expan>t</expan>i</expan>
                                                Egidii.</ab>
</div>
